### Lấy danh sách Booking theo UserId
GET http://localhost:5000/api/Booking?UserId=1&IsActive=true
Accept: application/json

### Tạo mới Booking
POST http://localhost:5000/api/Booking
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "userId": 1,
  "tourId": 2,
  "selectedDepartureDate": "2024-07-01T00:00:00",
  "numberOfAdults": 2,
  "numberOfChildren": 1,
  "numberOfInfants": 0,
  "noteForTour": "Yêu cầu xe riêng",
  "totalPrice": 5000000,
  "depositAmount": 1000000,
  "remainingAmount": 4000000,
  "contract": "Hop dong so 01"
}

### Cập nhật Booking
PUT http://localhost:5000/api/Booking
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "bookingId": 1,
  "numberOfAdults": 3,
  "noteForTour": "Cập nhật số lượng người lớn",
  "totalPrice": 6000000
}

### Xoá mềm Booking
PATCH http://localhost:5000/api/Booking/soft-delete/1?userId=1
Accept: application/json 